task_description: In app osmand, Grant OsmAnd precise location access only while using the app, then zoom in to see the details of your current location.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Return to the main map view and search for the city of 'Oran' to view its location and details.
In app osmand, Check the history tab to see if the location 'Vaduz' has been previously searched.
In app osmand, Search for a file named 'window_dump.xml' using the search bar.
In app osmand, Return to the main map view and then zoom in to the location of 'São Tomé and Príncipe'.
In app osmand, Zoom out the map until the entire African continent is visible.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Dismiss the location access request and then zoom in on the map to view the details of a specific city.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Scroll up to view the city of Madrid, Spain, then zoom in to see the surrounding area and identify major roads and landmarks.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Enable the display of public transport routes on the map by toggling the 'Transport' option.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Zoom out the map until the entire African continent is visible.
In app osmand, Open the 'window_dump.xml' file created on 'Mar 19, 10.10 kB, XML document' after filtering for documents.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Configure the map to show transport information and POI overlays.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Search for 'Paris' and then zoom in to street level to view the Eiffel Tower.
In app osmand, Find the nearest 'Cafe and restaurant' using the categories search and then view its details.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Scroll down the map to locate the country of Namibia and then zoom in to view the capital city of Windhoek.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Center the map on the current location, which is Algeria, and then zoom in to view nearby points of interest.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Zoom in on the map until the scale is 10 miles, then drag the map to center the city of Algiers.
In app osmand, Grant OsmAnd precise location access only while using the app.
In app osmand, Browse online photos of Algeria to find a picture of the Sahara Desert.
In app osmand, Return to the main OsmAnd interface and then search for a nearby restaurant.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Search for a specific address using the search bar.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Check if there are any track files available and import them if needed.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Return to the map view and zoom in to the current location to view nearby points of interest.
In app osmand, Search for a track named 'test' and determine if it exists.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Search for an address by first specifying the city/town/locality, then entering the street address and number.
In app osmand, Find the population of Algeria by clicking the 'DETAILS' button and navigating to the population information.
In app osmand, Import the 'window_dump.xml' file from the recent files into the OsmAnd app.
In app osmand, Enable the POI overlay, Transport, Tracks, and Wikipedia features on the map.
In app osmand, Find the location of 'Vaduz' by typing it into the address bar and selecting it from the search results.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Zoom in on the map of Antarctica until you can clearly see the coastline and major geographical features.
In app osmand, Zoom out until the entire African continent is visible on the map.
In app osmand, Task-Oriented: Search for 'London' and then zoom in to street level to view specific buildings.
